    "content_hash": "12b8ca4a16b76e01",
    "department": "Growth",
    "description": "ABOUT ELEVENLABS\n\nElevenLabs is an AI research and product company transforming how we interact with technology.\n\nWe launched in January 2023 with the first human-like AI voice model. Today, we serve millions of users and thousands of businesses - from fast-growing startups to large enterprises like Deutsche Telekom and Meta. Our investors are some of the world's most prominent, including Andreessen Horowitz, ICONIQ Growth and Sequoia. We've raised $781M in funding and our last valuation was $11B - multiples of 11, always.\n\nWe have expanded from voice into three main platforms:\n\n - ElevenAgents enables businesses to deliver seamless and intelligent customer experiences, with the integrations, testing, monitoring, and reliability necessary to deploy voice and chat agents at scale.\n\n - ElevenCreative empowers creators and marketers to generate and edit speech, music, image, and video across 70+ languages.\n\n - ElevenAPI gives developers access to our leading AI audio foundational models.\n\nEverything we do is the result of the creativity and commitment of our team - builders doing the best work of their lives. We are researchers, engineers, and operators. IOI medalists and ex-founders. If you want to work hard and create lasting positive impact, we want to hear from you.\n\n\nHOW WE WORK\n\n - High-velocity: Rapid experimentation, lean autonomous teams, and minimal bureaucracy.\n\n - Impact not job titles: We don’t have job titles. Instead, it’s about the impact you have. No task is above or beneath you.\n\n - AI first: We use AI to move faster with higher-quality results. We do this across the whole company—from engineering to growth to operations.\n\n - Excellence everywhere: Everything we do should match the quality of our AI models.\n\n - Global team: We prioritize your talent, not your location.\n\n\nWHAT WE OFFER\n\n - Innovative culture: You’ll be part of a generational opportunity to define the trajectory of AI, surrounded by a team pushing the boundaries of what’s possible.\n\n - Growth paths: Joining ElevenLabs means joining a dynamic team with countless opportunities to drive impact - beyond your immediate role and responsibilities.\n\n - Learning \u0026 development: ElevenLabs proactively supports professional development through an annual discretionary stipend.\n\n - Social travel: We also provide an annual discretionary stipend to meet up with colleagues each year, however you choose.\n\n - Annual company offsite: Each year, we bring the entire team together in a new location - past offsites have included Croatia and Italy.\n\n - Co-working: If you’re not located near one of our main hubs, we offer a monthly co-working stipend.\n\n\nABOUT THE ROLE\n\nWe’re looking for a Social Media Creator to take full ownership of ElevenLabs’ Instagram and TikTok presence. We already have a highly engaged audience of creators across Youtube, Linkedin, X and Instagram. Now, we’re focused on further deepening our impact across short-form content for Instagram (where we recently crossed 100K followers) and TikTok, scaling those channels in a meaningful, long-term way.\n\nThis role is about building and growing accounts that people genuinely want to follow. You’ll be responsible for strategy, execution, and growth, working across copywriting, content creation, experimentation, and community-building while representing the ElevenLabs brand at a very high standard.\n\nYou’ll have a high degree of autonomy, frequent opportunities to collaborate with some of the world’s leading AI creators, and the chance to make a visible, lasting impact on how ElevenLabs shows up to the creator community.\n\n\nWHAT YOU’LL DO\n\n - Own the strategy, content and day-to-day execution for ElevenLabs’ Instagram and TikTok accounts. (and YouTube Shorts)\n\n - Develop and test content ideas that resonate with creators and creatives globally.\n\n - Write compelling scripts and copy, shaping narratives that feel native to each platform.\n\n - Work with internal teams and external creators to produce high-quality static and video content.\n\n - Experiment with formats, trends, and growth tactics to continuously improve reach and engagement.\n\n - Build and nurture an engaged community through comments, DMs, and creator interactions.\n\n - Track performance, learn from data, and iterate quickly based on what works.\n\n\nWHO YOU ARE\n\nWe’re looking for someone who is deeply excited about social growth and creator culture, and who takes pride in building things from the ground up. You’ll thrive in this role if you:\n\n - Are or have previously been a creator with above 10k followers.\n\n - Are passionate about audio AI and excited by the opportunity to make creative tools more accessible worldwide.\n\n - Are highly motivated, self-directed, and comfortable taking ownership from day one.\n\n - Care deeply about quality and consistently aim to exceed expectations.\n\n - Think analytically about growth, experimentation, and distribution, not just content creation.\n\n - Move quickly, learn fast, and adapt easily in a fast-changing environment.\n\n - Work autonomously, take initiative, and leave ego at the door.\n   \n\n\nWHAT YOU BRING\n\nRequired\n\n - You’ve scaled at least one Instagram or TikTok account to 50k+ followers.\n\nNice to have\n\n - You’ve grown multiple accounts (your own or for companies/creators), or worked in social media roles where growth was a core responsibility.\n\n - Strong scriptwriting and copywriting skills with a sharp sense for what performs on social platforms.\n\n - Experience ideating and producing static and video content (hands-on creation is a strong bonus).\n\n - A strong intuition for trends, formats, and cultural moments on Instagram and TikTok. Comfort experimenting, failing fast, and doubling down on what works.\n\n - Comfortable with being on camera to entertain and educate viewers in an engaging way.\n\nThis is a highly creative role with real ownership and impact — ideal for someone who wants to build iconic social channels at one of the most exciting AI companies in the world.\n\n\nLOCATION\n\nThis role is remote and can be executed globally. If you prefer, you can work from our offices in Bangalore, Dublin, London, New York, San Francisco, Tokyo, and Warsaw.\n\n#LI-remote",
